event DomainRegistered(bytes32 indexed domainSeparator, bytes domainValue)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)

function executeEIP712(tuple(address from, address to, address token, uint256 txGas, uint256 tokenGasPrice, uint256 batchId, uint256 batchNonce, uint256 deadline, bytes data) req, bytes32 domainSeparator, bytes sig) returns (bool success, bytes ret)

function executePersonalSign(tuple(address from, address to, address token, uint256 txGas, uint256 tokenGasPrice, uint256 batchId, uint256 batchNonce, uint256 deadline, bytes data) req, bytes sig) returns (bool success, bytes ret)
function getNonce(address from, uint256 batchId) view returns (uint256)

function verifyEIP712(tuple(address from, address to, address token, uint256 txGas, uint256 tokenGasPrice, uint256 batchId, uint256 batchNonce, uint256 deadline, bytes data) req, bytes32 domainSeparator, bytes sig) view

function verifyPersonalSign(tuple(address from, address to, address token, uint256 txGas, uint256 tokenGasPrice, uint256 batchId, uint256 batchNonce, uint256 deadline, bytes data) req, bytes sig) view
